\ keep elements greater than 3
[ 1 2 3 4 5 ] [: 3 > :] filter .

\ keep none / keep all
[ 1 2 3 ] [: 100 > :] filter .
[ 1 2 3 ] [: 0 > :] filter .

\ empty source
[ ] [: 0 > :] filter .

\ filter over a set (members stay sorted)
{ 5 1 3 2 4 } [: 2 > :] filter .

\ composes with cardinality and map
[ 1 2 3 4 5 6 ] [: 3 > :] filter cardinality .
[ 1 2 3 4 ] [: 2 > :] filter [: dup * :] map .

\ failures
[ 1 2 3 ] 5 filter
5 [: 0 > :] filter
[ 1 2 3 ] [: dup :] filter
